display_name: RfxDocument transformation - 1000 - RAW test data sets_31 - Ariba Sourcing - 4

property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    'RFXDocument_' || "RfxDocument"."InternalId" as "ID",
    'SourcingProject_' || "RfxDocument"."ParentWorkspace_InternalId" AS "SourcingProject",
    CASE
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventType = '0' THEN 'Full Project'
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventType = '1' THEN 'RFI'
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventType = '2' THEN 'RFP'
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventType = '3' THEN 'RFQ'
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventType = '4' THEN 'Auction'
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventType = '5' THEN 'Survey'
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventType = '6' THEN 'Forward Auction' 
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventType = '7' THEN 'Sourcing Request'
    END AS EventTypeText,
    CASE 
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventState = 'NewState' THEN 'New State'
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventState = 'NotCreatedState' THEN 'Not Created State'
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventState = 'PendingSelectionState' THEN 'Pending Selection State'
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventState = 'ClosedState' THEN 'Closed State'
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventState = 'CancelledState' THEN 'Cancelled State'
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventState = 'OpenState' THEN 'Open State'
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventState = 'SubmittedState' THEN 'Submitted State'
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventState = 'ScheduledState' THEN 'Scheduled State'
        WHEN "RfxDocument".EventState = 'ArchivedState' THEN 'Archived State'
    END AS EventStateText,
    "RfxDocument"."InternalId" as "InternalId",
    cast("RfxDocument"."EventType" as int) as "EventType",
    "RfxDocument"."LastModified" as "LastModified",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,cast("RfxDocument"."TimeCreated" as Timestamp)) as "TimeCreated",
    "RfxDocument"."Status" as "Status",
    "RfxDocument"."IsPublishRequired" as "IsPublishRequired",
    "RfxDocument"."Active" as "Active",
    "RfxDocument"."Description" as "Description",
    "RfxDocument"."DocumentVersion" as "DocumentVersion",
    "RfxDocument"."EventState" as "EventState",
    "RfxDocument"."IsVersionPinned" as "IsVersionPinned",
    "RfxDocument"."Title" as "Title",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"RfxDocument"."TimeUpdated") as "TimeUpdated",
    "RfxDocument"."IsTest" as "IsTest",
    "RfxDocument"."Title_DefaultStringTranslation" as "TitleDefaultStringTranslation",
    "RfxDocument"."TemplateObject_InternalId" as "TemplateObjectInternalId",
    "RfxDocument"."ParentWorkspace_InternalId" as "ParentWorkspaceInternalId",
    "RfxDocument"."Content_ItemId" as "ContentItemId"
FROM "RfxDocument"
WHERE 1=1
    AND "RfxDocument"."Active" = 'true'
